text: Putten is a municipality in the province of Gelderland, Netherlands. It can also refer to: *Putten, a neighborhood in Eindhoven, Netherlands *Putten Island, former island now part of Voorne-Putten, an island in South Holland, Netherlands *Dutch surnames: **Van Putten **Van der Putten ==See also== *Putte (disambiguation)
